the audience is encouraged

00:03:12.910 --> 00:03:15.440
to ask questions
and offer comments.

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:19.000
Please be advised that your
voice and image may be recorded

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:21.480
and later broadcast
as part of this event.

00:03:21.480 --> 00:03:23.830
By participating in the
question and answer period,

00:03:23.830 --> 00:03:27.460
you are consenting to the
